summary: something i really enjoy about beau, besides her abrasiveness and moral compass and shit-eating grins, is how shameless she is....
body:
something i really enjoy about beau, besides her abrasiveness and moral compass and shit-eating grins, is how shameless she is. if beau wants something, she goes after it, and she doesn’t care what anybody thinks of her.

i didn’t realise how much i missed women like that in fiction

summary: Just starting to watch the new episode and I am at the art reel and I wanted to say that I think it’s really neat that they are...
body:
Just starting to watch the new episode and I am at the art reel and I wanted to say that I think it’s really neat that they are still including art from the first campaign in the art reels. It’s just really cool that even though it’s a new campaign they haven’t forgotten the old campaign, and that critters are still drawing characters from the old campaign, whether it be people rewatching or new critters catching up.

I dunno, I just really like that Vox Machina and the 115 episode story of their adventures is both remembered and still being discovered. That’s all.
